Coldkey

This is a special tool to generate a super safe private key for everiToken. It is specially designed for those who need very high security and guys who don't believe the wallet he / she is using.

Why it's safe

For safety, we use four ways to gain enough entropy:

  • Device's cryptography-strong hardware entropy based on OS's API (according to device's voltage, temperature, status of mainboard / cpu and so on)
  • User-specific entropy based on your browser and network
  • CPU entropy based on your CPU performance
  • Environment entropy based on your system environment

The security of generating private keys was reviewd by many block chain's implement including EOS. And we make it even much safer ever. It's really safe.

Create New Key

Important Note

  • Never forget your password.
  • Before clicking "New Key", make sure there is no network connected.
  • Don't use copy / paste to save your Mnemoinc if your system is not clean. Write it down. Check if it contains 24 words. Copy public key is safe.
  • Please save your Mnemoinc and public key carefully and make at least 2 backups for it!
  • Don't store your keys in unlocked place such as your desktop.
  • Double-check the full text of your Mnemoinc!
  • Please do the following after running:
    • Check your mnemoinc typo by typing these words in "validate mnemoinc" section.
    • Close this window / browser
    • Delete browser's cache
    • Reboot your device before reconnecting to the Internet.
